<% content_for :title, "About - Clough for SC5" %>

<%# Hero Section %>
<div class="bg-navy-900 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-4">
          Meet Andrew<br/>Clough
        </h1>
        <p class="text-campaign-gold text-xl font-semibold">Republican Candidate for SC House District 5</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="w-72 h-72 md:w-96 md:h-96 bg-navy-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-8xl">👤</span>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-campaign-red text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold">
            District 5
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# His Story Section %>
<section class="py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="text-campaign-red font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">His Story</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-6">
          A lifetime of<br/>service to District 5
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-navy-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Andrew Clough is a lifelong resident of Rock Hill, South Carolina, and a proud conservative
          running to represent the people of District 5 in the State House.
        </p>
        <p>
          Growing up in York County, Andrew learned the values that matter: hard work, faith, family,
          and dedication to community. After graduating from local schools, he built his career while
          staying deeply involved in serving his neighbors.
        </p>
        <p>
          Andrew has seen firsthand how Columbia's policies affect everyday families in District 5.
          From rising property taxes to struggling schools, he knows the challenges residents face —
          because he faces them too.
        </p>
        <p>
          Now, Andrew is ready to take his experience and values to the State House to fight for
          the people who elected him.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# Why I'm Running Section %>
<section class="bg-ivory-50 py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-campaign-red font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">Why I'm Running</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-6">
        I believe District 5 deserves better.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-navy-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Our community has so much potential, but Columbia keeps holding us back. I decided to run
        because I knew I could make a real difference — not for myself, but for every family in
        District 5 who deserves a representative who will actually fight for them.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-campaign-red/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-campaign-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Lower Taxes</h3>
        <p class="text-navy-600">
          You work hard for your money. I believe you should keep more of it. I'll fight to cut
          wasteful spending and oppose tax hikes.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-campaign-red/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-campaign-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Better Education</h3>
        <p class="text-navy-600">
          Parents know what's best for their kids. I'll advocate for school choice and policies
          that put students first.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-campaign-red/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-campaign-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Smaller Government</h3>
        <p class="text-navy-600">
          The best government is the one that stays out of your way. I'll fight regulations
          that hurt families and small businesses.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# Family Section %>
<section class="py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-campaign-red font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">Family</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-6">
        Family is everything
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-40 h-40 bg-navy-200 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-5xl">👨‍👩‍👧</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-navy-900">With My Wife</h3>
        <p class="text-navy-600 text-sm">Kate has been my rock for over 20 years</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-40 h-40 bg-navy-200 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-5xl">👧</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-navy-900">Addison, 14</h3>
        <p class="text-navy-600 text-sm">Our oldest daughter</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-40 h-40 bg-navy-200 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-5xl">👦</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-navy-900">Myles, 12</h3>
        <p class="text-navy-600 text-sm">Our son</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-40 h-40 bg-navy-200 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-5xl">👦</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-navy-900">Wyatt, 10</h3>
        <p class="text-navy-600 text-sm">Our youngest</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <p class="text-navy-700 text-lg">
        Andrew and Kate also have two grown children: Tammy and Troy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# CTA Section %>
<section class="bg-navy-900 text-white py-16">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
      Join our team
    </h2>
    <p class="text-navy-200 text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Help us bring conservative leadership to District 5. Your support can make the difference.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <%= link_to "Volunteer", volunteer_path, class: "bg-campaign-red hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors" %>
      <a href="#" class="border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-navy-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
        Donate
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

